{"id": "geq1665702595169", "title": "Controlling the Load Order of JavaScript and CSS", "breadcrumbs": ["Developing Web Applications", "Dynamic Server Pages", "Executing Logic in the Browser", "Controlling the Load Order of JavaScript and CSS"], "url": "https://docs.rocketsoftware.com/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/geq1665702595169.html", "html": "<html><body><header class=\"zDocsTopicPageHead\"><h1 class=\"css-g931ng\">Controlling the Load Order of JavaScript and CSS</h1><div class=\"zDocsTopicActions\" role=\"list\"><div class=\"zDocsBundlePagination\" data-testid=\"next-prev-container\" role=\"listitem\"><div class=\"zDocsPrevTopicButton zDocsPrevTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Previous:   Read-Only Fields in Dynamic Server Pages \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Previous:   Read-Only Fields in Dynamic Server Pages \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dsa1665702583839.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-prev\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-prev\"></use></svg></a></span></div><div class=\"zDocsNextTopicButton zDocsNextTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Next:   Generating HTML class Attributes for Styling \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Next:   Generating HTML class Attributes for Styling \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/woq1665702862912.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></a></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsMyDocsMenu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Add to My Topics\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Add to My Topics\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" id=\"addToMyDocsDropdownTrigger\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg>Add to My Topics</span><div aria-labelledby=\"pdfDropdown\" class=\"dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-right\"><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/geq1665702595169.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub\">Add selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/geq1665702595169.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub_head\">Add Topic &amp; Subtopics with topic head</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/geq1665702595169.html?finish_action=mydocs_pub\">Add entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsWatchButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Watch\" class=\"d-lg-flex d-none zDocsSubscribeButton\" data-tooltip-content=\"Watch\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsSubscribeButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye zDocsSubscribeButton\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsSubscribeButton\">Watch</span></span></div><div class=\"zDocsExportPdfMenu zDocsExportMenu\" data-testid=\"export-pdf-menu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Download PDF\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Download PDF\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#ZdExportPDFModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2527822\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2527822\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Dez 28, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104geq1665702595169.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/geq1665702595169.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/geq1665702595169.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"geq1665702595169\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                       \n Controlling the Load Order of JavaScript and CSS \n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body taskbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">It is possible to insert your own JavaScript and CSS into the HTML that Uniface generates for dynamic server pages.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section context\" id=\"geq1665702595169__context_w1144ab1b5b1_w1145ab1b5_w1146ab1\">\n<div class=\"div context\" id=\"geq1665702595169__topic_d21278e1_d21279e1_d21280e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"geq1665702595169__p_d21281e1_d21282e1_d21283e1\">At runtime, Uniface generates the HTML for the DSP web page based definitions in the DSP. The first time the complete page is generated, this includes references to the JavaScript files required for the Uniface runtime engine, and CSS files required for formatting the page. By default, these references are inserted just before the closing tag of the header (<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;/head&gt;</code>).</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"geq1665702595169__p_d21284e1_d21285e1_d21286e1\">However, you may require external JavaScript and styles that need to be loaded in a specific order and location, and which may have dependencies on the Uniface files.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"geq1665702595169__p_d21287e1_d21288e1_d21289e1\">To control the order in which all JavaScript and CSS is loaded:</p>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section><ol class=\"ol steps\"><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"geq1665702595169__li_d10349e1_d10350e1_d10351e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\" id=\"geq1665702595169__p_d21290e1_d21291e1_d21292e1\">Edit the DSP layout and insert your CSS and\n               JavaScript, or references to files containing this code, at the desired locations in\n               the layout. </span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<p class=\"p\">Use <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;script&gt;</code> tags to insert the desired JavaScript or a\n                  reference to the JavaScript file. For example:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">&lt;script src=\"myscripts.js\"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"geq1665702595169__p_d21293e1_d21294e1_d21295e1\">Use <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;style&gt;</code> tags or links\n                  to CSS files to insert the desired styles in the header. For example:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">&lt;link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"../css/mycss.css\" /&gt;</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"geq1665702595169__p_d21296e1_d21297e1_d21298e1\">For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qpq1665702595271.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qpq1665702595271.html\" title=\"You can create your own JavaScript definitions using your preferred editor. However, the operations or triggers must be made available in the runtime component.\">Implementing External Client-Side Triggers and Operations</a>. </p>\n</div>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"geq1665702595169__li_d10352e1_d10353e1_d10354e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">To control where the Uniface JS and CSS file references are inserted, enter placeholders for the Uniface JavaScript and CSS locations:\n </span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"geq1665702595169__li_d10355e1_d10356e1_d10357e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;!--$UNIFACEJS--&gt;</code> for JavaScript\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"geq1665702595169__li_d10358e1_d10359e1_d10360e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;!--$UNIFACECSS--&gt;</code> for CSS\n </li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"geq1665702595169__note_w1150ab1b5b3b3b3b3_w1151ab1b5b3b3b3_w1152ab1b5b3b3_w1153ab1b5b3_w1154ab1b5_w1155ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> The placeholders are not case sensitive, but they must not contain spaces.</div>\n</div>\n</li></ol></section>\n<section class=\"section result body required-cleanup-multiple-ol-elements-in-topic-body\" id=\"geq1665702595169__result_w1147ab1b5b5_w1148ab1b5_w1149ab1\">\n<div class=\"sectiondiv\">\n<p class=\"p\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Example: DSP Layout with JavaScript Insertions</strong></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<ol class=\"ol\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"geq1665702595169__li_d10361e1_d10362e1_d10363e1\">Link to default Uniface style sheet.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"geq1665702595169__li_d10364e1_d10365e1_d10366e1\">Placeholder for stylesheets required by widgets.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"geq1665702595169__li_d10367e1_d10368e1_d10369e1\">Custom script insertion that references\n                     <span class=\"ph filepath\">myscripts.js</span>. <div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"geq1665702595169__note_w1156ab1b5b5b1b3b5b3_w1157ab1b5b5b1b3b5_w1158ab1b5b5b1b3_w1159ab1b5b5b1_w1160ab1b5b5_w1161ab1b5_w1162ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> The location of these\n                     files can be configured using the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$UNIFACE_RUNTIME_BASE_URL</span>\n                     assignment setting. Files are assumed to be relative to this location.</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"geq1665702595169__li_d10370e1_d10371e1_d10372e1\">Placeholder for Uniface JavaScript files, including the Uniface runtime engine and widgets.\n </li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\n&lt;html lang=\"en\"&gt;\n &lt;head&gt;\n &lt;meta name=\"Default\" content=\"Uniface 10\" /&gt;\n &lt;link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"../css/uniface.css\" /&gt; <a class=\"xref\" href=\"#geq1665702595169__li_d10361e1_d10362e1_d10363e1\">1</a>\n &lt;!--$UNIFACECSS--&gt; <a class=\"xref\" href=\"#geq1665702595169__li_d10364e1_d10365e1_d10366e1\">2</a>\n &lt;title&gt;title&lt;/title&gt;\n &lt;/head&gt;\n &lt;body&gt;\n &lt;table id=\"uent:NM.NME\" border=\"1\"&gt;\n ...\n &lt;/table&gt;\n &lt;script src=\"myscripts.js\"&gt;&lt;/script&gt; <a class=\"xref\" href=\"#geq1665702595169__li_d10367e1_d10368e1_d10369e1\">3</a>\n &lt;!--$UNIFACEJS--&gt; <a class=\"xref\" href=\"#geq1665702595169__li_d10370e1_d10371e1_d10372e1\">4</a>\n &lt;/body&gt;\n&lt;/html&gt;\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sectiondiv\">\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"https://learn.rocketsoftware.com/course/view.php?id=71\" rel=\"external noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"Learn More\" class=\"image\" id=\"geq1665702595169__image_gjd_tn4_vdc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/My_Learn_More_Button.jpg?_LANG=enus\"/></a></p>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sif1665702784304.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$UNIFACE_RUNTIME_BASE_URL</a><p>Specify the URL where the runtime JavaScript and CSS files for Uniface are located.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527822\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527822\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Controlling the Load Order of JavaScript and CSS Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Dez 28, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Controlling the Load Order of JavaScript and CSS It is possible to insert your own JavaScript and CSS into the HTML that Uniface generates for dynamic server pages. At runtime, Uniface generates the HTML for the DSP web page based definitions in the DSP. The first time the complete page is generated, this includes references to the JavaScript files required for the Uniface runtime engine, and CSS files required for formatting the page. By default, these references are inserted just before the closing tag of the header ( </head> ). However, you may require external JavaScript and styles that need to be loaded in a specific order and location, and which may have dependencies on the Uniface files. To control the order in which all JavaScript and CSS is loaded: Edit the DSP layout and insert your CSS and JavaScript, or references to files containing this code, at the desired locations in the layout. Use <script> tags to insert the desired JavaScript or a reference to the JavaScript file. For example: <script src=\"myscripts.js\"></script> Copy Use <style> tags or links to CSS files to insert the desired styles in the header. For example: <link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"../css/mycss.css\" /> Copy For more information, see Implementing External Client-Side Triggers and Operations . To control where the Uniface JS and CSS file references are inserted, enter placeholders for the Uniface JavaScript and CSS locations: <!--$UNIFACEJS--> for JavaScript <!--$UNIFACECSS--> for CSS Note: The placeholders are not case sensitive, but they must not contain spaces. Example: DSP Layout with JavaScript Insertions Link to default Uniface style sheet. Placeholder for stylesheets required by widgets. Custom script insertion that references myscripts.js . Note: The location of these files can be configured using the $UNIFACE_RUNTIME_BASE_URL assignment setting. Files are assumed to be relative to this location. Placeholder for Uniface JavaScript files, including the Uniface runtime engine and widgets. <!DOCTYPE html> <html lang=\"en\"> <head> <meta name=\"Default\" content=\"Uniface 10\" /> <link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"../css/uniface.css\" /> 1 <!--$UNIFACECSS--> 2 <title>title</title> </head> <body> <table id=\"uent:NM.NME\" border=\"1\"> ... </table> <script src=\"myscripts.js\"></script> 3 <!--$UNIFACEJS--> 4 </body> </html> Copy Related Links $UNIFACE_RUNTIME_BASE_URL Specify the URL where the runtime JavaScript and CSS files for Uniface are located. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}